d touch.\n\n• Complete rationale for EVERY CFA exam question. You will understand \"why\" an answer is correct.\n\nWorld\'s LARGEST CFA exam question database!\n\n• NEW! See your personal performance ranking vs. other CFA exam candidates worldwide.\n\n• Every CFA Institute Learning Outcome is answered.\n\n• Expert authors in each subject (not generalists).\n\n• Take unlimited mock tests in all subject areas, or target selected subjects.\n\n• Comparison Statistics: Know where you stand vs. other CFA candidates worldwide.\n\n• Automatic Content Updates: You will always have the latest CFA exam questions.\n\n• Seen Least Option: Avoid repeating questions.\n\n• Missed Most Option: Review the questions you\'ve missed most often.\n\n• Favorite Option: Flag specific CFA exam questions for review later.\n\n• Question Timer: Avoid running out of time on exam day.\n\nADAPTIVE LEARNING TECHNOLOGY: TestBank is continually re-calibrated every time you answer a question, based on your personal performance.\n\n• Rationale for every single question\nThis makes CFA TestBank truly stand-alone. You will not need to refer to another source while you are using TestBank. Your learning will be more efficient and productive since everything you need to know is in front of you.\n\n• You choose which subjects to study\nDepending on your learning needs or time frame, you can decide to take a specific number of questions randomly selected from ALL of the subject areas, any COMBINATION of the subjects, or an INDIVIDUAL subject.\n\n• Your performance is tracked\nYour performance is displayed when you open the app, allowing you to track your progress and target your studies.\n\n• Questions Seen Least\nTestBank knows which questions you have answered the least often. When you choose this option, the questions that you have seen the least number of times will display first.\n\nAllen CFA Exam Review:\n\n •Simulates actual test-taking\n •Keeps you focused\n •Saves you time\n •Strengthens your weak areas\n •Reinforces your strong areas\n •Tracks your progress\n •Solidifies concepts\n •Improves your memory\n •Familiarizes you with past questions\n •Makes your studying efficient\n •Builds your confidence\n________\n\nWe love hearing from you! Don\'t hesitate to contact us if you have any CFA exam prep questions, issues, or suggestions.\n\nAllen Resources | CFA Exam Prep Since 1993\nWeb: AllenResources.com\nTwitter: @AllenCFA\nEmail: Pass@AllenResources.com\nPhone: 401.965.0340\n______\n\nCFA Institute does not endorse, promote, or warrant the accuracy or quality of the products or services offered by Allen Resources, Inc. CFA Institute, CFA® and Chartered Financial Analyst® are trademarks owned by CFA Institute.', '2011-06-05 05:27:13', '2014-05-24 15:01:56')" in /var/www/html/analozy/fuel/core/classes/database/pdo/connection.php on line 175
